channel.description:
ok so i just downloaded this and when i start my server and try to login it says server: client handler accepted from: my ip and port did not save for: my username server: client handler: my username disconnected
also it says in login box... 'you are already logged in try again now, or make another name' when i havent even logged in yet! help me plz thanks in advance! :)

item.title: Already signed in?!?
item.dc:creator: @djdoyle1 djdoyle1
item.description:
@djdoyle1 wrote:

What’s happening here is you have the wrong type a client. This is why it is not saving. When you login it will null your server. A simple way to stop this is change client.
